responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "0BA4F17A43E808EB4338C897A5C6A426", "Look westward across the river. There rests the Floral Isle, an enchanted spot of land where the granduer of the Zanis Willow rules. It\'s presence gives life to a wide variety of flowers on the isle, some of which only exist there.")
